items.title: Awesome Arcgis Developers
items.content_text:
### Starter apps and CLIs

*   [awesome-arcgis (⭐26)](https://github.com/esri-es/awesome-arcgis/) - Awesome list with a wiki flavor with resources about Esri and ArcGIS organized by: products, industries, file formats, content providers, etc.
*   [awesome-earthobservation-code (⭐1.3k)](https://github.com/acgeospatial/awesome-earthobservation-code) - Tools, tutorials, code, helpful projects and links about Earth Observation and Geospatial stuff.
*   [awesome-geojson (⭐2.4k)](https://github.com/tmcw/awesome-geojson) - GeoJSON utilities: operations,editors & viewers, validation, services, conversion, etc.
*   [awesome-geospatial (⭐4.5k)](https://github.com/sacridini/Awesome-Geospatial) - Databases, radar, lidar, web map development, etc.
*   [awesome-gis (⭐4.9k)](https://github.com/sshuair/awesome-gis) - GIS, remote sensing, 3D apps, Web Map Servers, Geospatial libraries, Open Standards, data, etc.
*   [awesome-json-datasets (⭐3.5k)](https://github.com/jdorfman/awesome-json-datasets) - JSON datasets that don't require authentication about: climate, crime, goverment, NASA, travel, etc.
*   [awesome-open-geoscience (⭐1.6k)](https://github.com/softwareunderground/awesome-open-geoscience) - Curated from repositories that make our lives as geoscientists, hackers, and data wranglers easier or just more awesome.
*   [awesome-public-datasets (⭐64k)](https://github.com/awesomedata/awesome-public-datasets) - A topic-centric list of high-quality open datasets.
*   [awesome-remote-sensing-change-detection (⭐1.9k)](https://github.com/wenhwu/awesome-remote-sensing-change-detection) - List of datasets, codes, and contests related to remote sensing change detection.
*   [awesome-satellite-imagery-datasets (⭐3.8k)](https://github.com/chrieke/awesome-satellite-imagery-datasets) - List of satellite image training datasets with annotations for computer vision and deep learning.
*   [awesome-semantic-segmentation (⭐11k)](https://github.com/mrgloom/awesome-semantic-segmentation) - Networks by architecture (semantic segmentation, instance aware segmentation, etc.), RNN, GANS, datasets, and more.
*   [awesome-vector-tiles (⭐2.5k)](https://github.com/mapbox/awesome-vector-tiles) - Implementations of the Mapbox Vector Tile specification: parsers & generators, clients, apps and command line tools, CLI utilities, servers, etc.
items.content_html:
Starter apps and CLIs

  • awesome-arcgis (⭐26) - Awesome list with a wiki flavor with resources about Esri and ArcGIS organized by: products, industries, file formats, content providers, etc.
  • awesome-earthobservation-code (⭐1.3k) - Tools, tutorials, code, helpful projects and links about Earth Observation and Geospatial stuff.
  • awesome-geojson (⭐2.4k) - GeoJSON utilities: operations,editors & viewers, validation, services, conversion, etc.
  • awesome-geospatial (⭐4.5k) - Databases, radar, lidar, web map development, etc.
  • awesome-gis (⭐4.9k) - GIS, remote sensing, 3D apps, Web Map Servers, Geospatial libraries, Open Standards, data, etc.
  • awesome-json-datasets (⭐3.5k) - JSON datasets that don't require authentication about: climate, crime, goverment, NASA, travel, etc.
  • awesome-open-geoscience (⭐1.6k) - Curated from repositories that make our lives as geoscientists, hackers, and data wranglers easier or just more awesome.
  • awesome-public-datasets (⭐64k) - A topic-centric list of high-quality open datasets.
  • awesome-remote-sensing-change-detection (⭐1.9k) - List of datasets, codes, and contests related to remote sensing change detection.
  • awesome-satellite-imagery-datasets (⭐3.8k) - List of satellite image training datasets with annotations for computer vision and deep learning.
  • awesome-semantic-segmentation (⭐11k) - Networks by architecture (semantic segmentation, instance aware segmentation, etc.), RNN, GANS, datasets, and more.
  • awesome-vector-tiles (⭐2.5k) - Implementations of the Mapbox Vector Tile specification: parsers & generators, clients, apps and command line tools, CLI utilities, servers, etc.
